From @euhmeuh initial version.
Print text using flowers for slack.

Works with the alphabet, space and exclamation point.

Usage: flowers.py [-h] [--spaced] t

Print some flowers.

positional arguments:
  t           The text to print (currently supports English alphabet only)

optional arguments:
  -h, --help  show this help message and exit
  --spaced    Spaces between letters (default: False)

